&lt;p&gt;This community post is an opportunity for an enthusiastic and self-motivated registered or newly qualified General Nurse to work within City Health Care Partnership CIC,&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Neighborhood care team provides holistic quality nursing care to a dedicated client group who need support and care with Long Term Conditions management /complex wound care /palliative care. Care is delivered in patients own environment or a treatment room.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team has a multidisciplinary approach and works closely with other local providers and other healthcare providers within the East Riding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We welcome interested candidates for an informal visit.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Further information and enquires please contact Denise Long Clinical Team Leader&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;T: 01262 423183 | M: 07919544603 | Email: deniselong2@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
